1 whether the prospective adoptive parent has had parental rights to
2 a child terminated in Oklahoma this state or whether the
3 prospective adoptive parent has relinquished parental rights to a
4 child in Oklahoma this state.
5 F. Nothing in this section shall be construed as prohibiting
6 the Department from disclosing such confidential information as may
7 be necessary to secure appropriate care, treatment, protection, or
8 supervision of a child alleged to be abused or neglected.
